Organization of Petroleum Exporting Countries in 2011, Saudi
Arabian Oil Minister Ali al-Naimi told reporters after an OPEC
meeting in Vienna today. Iranian minister Masoud Mir-Kazemi was
expected to hold the post next year after being named as OPECâ€™s
